videos.headline: T. Pigrome pass intercepted,K. Hardin
videos.description: Tyrrell Pigrome pass intercepted KiAnte Hardin

videos.headline: Smith spins for 8-yard touchdown
videos.description: Rodney Smith looks to be contained but spins away from the Maryland defense to give Minnesota a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Gophers score on perfectly executed screen pass
videos.description: Conor Rhoda hits Shannon Brooks with a screen pass that he takes 17 yards for the touchdown to extend Minnesota's lead to 14-0 over Maryland.

videos.headline: Smith breaks loose for 70-yard run, second TD
videos.description: Rodney Smith blasts by the Maryland defense and scores a 70-yard touchdown to give Minnesota a 24-3 lead.

videos.headline: T. Pigrome pass,to D. Moore for 11 yds for a TD
videos.description: Tyrrell Pigrome pass complete to D.J. Moore for 11 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Minnesota turns tipped pass into 82-yard pick-six
videos.description: With Maryland driving into the red zone, Antoine Winfield makes the interception and goes 82 yards the other direction to seal the win for Minnesota.
